page.title: 09BROWNIES IN BAMFORD. 2
page.content: MRS SUTTON ALSO SENDS NOTES TO MUMS TO TELL THEM WHERE WE HAVE GONE. IF WE GO SOMEWHERE SHE ALWAYS TAKES FIRST_AID WHERE EVER WE GO.THE COMMISSIONER ORGANISES THE BIG OUTINGS.MRS. SUTTON SAID " NO I DON'T THINK THAT ALL THE BROWNIES IN THE COUNTRY GO TO MEETINGS ON A MONDAY".ALL THE BROWNIES IN THE WORLD DO NOT WEAR THE SAME UNIFORM.BROWN OWL COULD NOT KEEP COUNT OF THE BADGES.THERE ARE ABOUT 20 BROWNIES IN THE BAMFORD PACK.SHE THINKS THAT THE BROWNIES BEHAVIOUR IS VERY GOOD.HER FAVOURITE GAME IS ' STRUT MISS LUCY. ' .................
